quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  69,38,"Ee mayee, waxaan ku dhaartay waxa aad aragtaan"
  69,39,Iyo wax aydaan aragba
  69,40,Hubaal waa hadal (Ilaahay) uu keenay Rasuul sharaf leh
  69,41,"Oo ma aha hadal gabyaa, yaraa inta aad rumeysaan"
  69,42,"ama hadal curraafle, yaraa inta aad waantowdaan"
  69,43,Waa waxyi ka yimid xagga Rabbiga uunanka
  69,44,Oo haddii uu naga been sheegi lahaa
  69,45,Waxaan hubaal ku qaban laheyn gacanta Midig
  69,46,Markaas waxaan hubaal goyn laheyn halbowlaha
  69,47,Oo ma jiro axad idinka mid ahi oo naga celin lahaa isaga
  69,48,Oo xaqiiq waa u waano kuwaa ka dhowrsada xumaha
  69,49,Oo xaqiiq waan ognahay inay qaarkiin yihiin xaq diidayaal
  69,50,Oo xaqiiq waa u murugo iyo ciil gaalada
  69,51,Oo hubaal waa xaq dhab ah
  69,52,"Ee huf oo xurmee Magaca Rabbigaa,Weynaha"